    • Constructor Detail

      • SpiButtonTool

        public SpiButtonTool(MapView mapView,
                     android.widget.ImageButton button,
                     int index)
        This tool is similar to the SelectPointButtonTool, but only one instance of each button should exist, making it easy to define. Unlike the SelectPointButtonTool, the SpiButtonTool needs to publish its information should it be turned on (enabled or disabled state). The index specified pulls the resources to draw the appropriate icon. Currently there are only 1, 2, and 3 available, but additional would simply be a matter of creating new resources. Perhaps these can be created on the fly at some point.
        Parameters:
        mapView - MapView used to construct this button
        button - Button to associated with this tool
        index -
